@{jleft}GrabURL requires @{"GrabHTTP" Link GrabHTTP.guide/main 0}, @{"UrlManager" Link UrlManager.guide/main 0} and @{"ScanHTML" Link ScanHTML.guide/main 0}.  You should have received those with this script.

